body.p: I do hereby return to the Hon. Roger S Greene, Chief Justice of the Territory of Washington, and Judge of the District Court holding terms at Seattle, that before the coming to me of the annexed writ, the said Charles Barnes was committed to my custody, and detained by virtue of another writ, a copy of which is hereto annexed, the original of which I also, herewith produce nevertheless I have the body of the said Charles Barnes before you at the day and place named in said annexed writ, as I am therein annexed
J.H. McGraw Sheriff, King County W.T.
Subscribed and Sworn to before me this 6th day of January, 1886
L.S. Booth Deputy King Co. W.T.
Bringing up petitioner 1.00 Copy of Commitment .80 Travel .20 Return .50 Total $2.50
